children.title: Welcome
children.content:
# Welcome to Documentation

Click the **Edit Documentation** button to add your content.

## deneme123

Start by creating sections and pages for your documentation.

### Features
- **Sections**: Organize your content into categories
- **Pages**: Add detailed documentation pages
- **Icons**: Add emojis or symbols to make navigation visual
- **Markdown**: Full markdown support with syntax highlighting
- **GitHub Integration**: Automatic saving to GitHub repository

### Quick Start
1. Click "Edit Documentation" (password: admin123)
2. Add new sections with "Add Section"
3. Add pages with "Add Page"
4. Click edit button to modify content
5. Save changes to update GitHub

Enjoy documenting! ðŸ“š
